OL,3,C'She cut me with scissors': Inside the
OL,4,CUK's underground cosmetic surgery
OL,5,Cnetwork
OL,7,FWarning: This video contains
OL,8,Fdistressing images
OL,10,FAn unregulated cosmetic business
OL,11,Fpreviously investigated by ITV News is
OL,12,Fstill operating out of residential
OL,13,Fbuildings, as Cree-Summer Haughton
OL,14,Freports
OL,16,FWhen Alysha told me about the moment
OL,17,Fshe saw scissors being brought towards
OL,18,Fher during a cosmetic surgery, I knew
OL,19,Fthis wasn't simply another story about
OL,20,Fa treatment gone wrong.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
