PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780045515
OL,3,C'She cut me with scissors': Inside the
OL,4,CUK's underground cosmetic surgery
OL,5,Cnetwork
OL,7,F"I remember just seeing the scissors
OL,8,Fand then them coming towards me - and
OL,9,Fthat was it," she told me.
OL,11,FI've been investigating the
OL,12,Funregulated cosmetic industry in the
OL,13,FUK for over three years now but still,
OL,14,Fwhen I heard scissors were used to
OL,15,Fperform a surgical treatment on an
OL,16,Fintimate area, I was shocked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780045515
OL,3,C'She cut me with scissors': Inside the
OL,4,CUK's underground cosmetic surgery
OL,5,Cnetwork
OL,7,FThe 27-year-old, who is from Wales,
OL,8,Fsaid she was left needing
OL,9,Freconstructive surgery after
OL,10,Fundergoing two cosmetic procedures
OL,11,Flinked to a business I had previously
OL,12,Finvestigated.
OL,14,FIn 2024, our undercover reporting
OL,15,Fexposed Luxury Medical Aesthetics, a
OL,16,Fcompany offering one-day liposuction
OL,17,Ftraining courses to people with no
OL,18,Fmedical background.
OL,20,FAs a result of our expose, it looked
OL,21,Fas though the operation had shut down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780045515
OL,3,C'She cut me with scissors': Inside the
OL,4,CUK's underground cosmetic surgery
OL,5,Cnetwork
OL,7,FOnline listings showed the business as
OL,8,Fpermanently closed and Companies House
OL,9,Frecords listed it as dissolved.
OL,11,FBut while investigating Alysha's case,
OL,12,FI found evidence that procedures
OL,13,Flinked to the same network may still
OL,14,Fbe continuing - but this time from
OL,15,Fresidential properties.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
