OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780045515
OL,3,C'She cut me with scissors': Inside the
OL,4,CUK's underground cosmetic surgery
OL,5,Cnetwork
OL,7,FAlysha told me her experience started
OL,8,Fthe same way many cosmetic journeys do
OL,9,F- through social media.
OL,11,F"Everything was really positive," she
OL,12,Fsaid of the reviews for London Medical
OL,13,FAesthetics, which despite the name,
OL,14,Fstill had the same branding as Luxury
OL,15,FMA.
OL,17,FAfter seeing videos and
OL,18,Frecommendations online, Alysha booked
OL,19,Fa labiaplasty with them - an intimate
OL,20,Fcosmetic procedure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780045515
OL,3,C'She cut me with scissors': Inside the
OL,4,CUK's underground cosmetic surgery
OL,5,Cnetwork
OL,7,FThis time the "surgeon" was a woman
OL,8,Fcalled Miss Cindy, also known as Luyen
OL,9,FVu or "The Liverpool Lady".
OL,11,FMiss Cindy appears to have little
OL,12,Fonline presence of her own. Instead,
OL,13,Fvideos of her work appear to spread
OL,14,Fthrough reposts, recommendations and
OL,15,Fword of mouth.
OL,17,FAcross TikTok and Instagram, the
OL,18,Freviews I saw were overwhelmingly
OL,19,Fpositive. But Alysha says alarm bells
OL,20,Fwent off the moment she arrived at the
OL,21,Faddress in London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780045515
OL,3,C'She cut me with scissors': Inside the
OL,4,CUK's underground cosmetic surgery
OL,5,Cnetwork
OL,7,F"When I arrived at the postcode there
OL,8,Fwas no salon," she said. "It was an
OL,9,Fapartment block."
OL,11,FWhen the procedure started, "she cut
OL,12,Fme with the scissors," Alysha said.
OL,13,F"By the time she had them in her hand
OL,14,Fand cut me, I was like: 'what?'"
OL,16,F"She doesn't draw, she doesn't
OL,17,Fmeasure... she just cuts."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780045515
OL,3,C'She cut me with scissors': Inside the
OL,4,CUK's underground cosmetic surgery
OL,5,Cnetwork
OL,7,FDespite what she describes as a
OL,8,Ftraumatic experience, Alysha says
OL,9,Fdiscounted prices and positive
OL,10,Frecommendations persuaded her this had
OL,11,Fbeen a one-off.
OL,13,FSo weeks later, she booked a mini
OL,14,Ffacelift directly with Miss Cindy
OL,15,Fagain, but this time the procedure was
OL,16,Fin Liverpool.
OL,18,F"That was probably the worst decision
OL,19,FI've made," she told me.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780045515
OL,3,C'She cut me with scissors': Inside the
OL,4,CUK's underground cosmetic surgery
OL,5,Cnetwork
OL,7,FThe facelift became infected and
OL,8,FAlysha said she had to eventually
OL,9,Ftravel to Turkey for reconstructive
OL,10,Fsurgery.
OL,12,F"(The doctor) had to reopen the wound,
OL,13,Fremove the stitches and clear the
OL,14,Finfection," she said.
OL,16,FITV News could find no record of Miss
OL,17,FCindy/Luyen Vu being registered with
OL,18,Fthe General Medical Council.
OL,26,@tD@BpmtD@Mpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780045515
OL,3,C'She cut me with scissors': Inside the
OL,4,CUK's underground cosmetic surgery
OL,5,Cnetwork
OL,7,FWe also did not receive a response
OL,8,Ffrom both Luyen Vu and Luxury Medical
OL,9,FAesthetics despite multiple requests
OL,10,Ffor comment.
OL,12,FI took our findings to consultant
OL,13,Fplastic surgeon, Dan Marsh, to see
OL,14,Fwhat the likelihood of being medically
OL,15,Ftrained is.
OL,17,FHe told me: "Anybody carrying out
OL,18,Fsurgery in a flat, in a non-clinical
OL,19,Fenvironment, shows they don't know
OL,20,Fwhat they're doing," he told me.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780045515
OL,3,C'She cut me with scissors': Inside the
OL,4,CUK's underground cosmetic surgery
OL,5,Cnetwork
OL,7,F"You shouldn't be allowed to carry out
OL,8,Fsurgery on a person unless you're
OL,9,Fappropriately trained."
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FAlysha said she wants others to think
OL,17,Fcarefully before being persuaded by
OL,18,Fonline recommendations and heavily
OL,19,Fdiscounted cosmetic procedures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
