CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780045515
OL,3,C'She cut me with scissors': Inside the
OL,4,CUK's underground cosmetic surgery
OL,5,Cnetwork
OL,7,F"There's a reason these procedures are
OL,8,Fso cheap," she said. "Nothing is worth
OL,9,Fhaving scars across your face for the
OL,10,Frest of your life."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
